Haryana
Dec 10, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 16-year-old girl was allegedly raped by a youth known to her, police said here today.

The alleged incident happened yesterday, they said adding a case had been registered but the youth was yet to be arrested.

The youth, who was known to the girl, a student of a coaching centre, lured her to a hotel located near Parijat Chowk and allegedly raped her, police said.

The girl narrated the incident to her family who approached the police.

In her complaint to police, the girl alleged the youth, hailing from Panchkula, threatened her if she reported the incident to anyone.

After the victim's medical examination, a case under section 376 (rape) of the IPC was registered, police said. 

